WEBVTT

00:01.600 --> 00:04.100
Previously on NYPD Blue.

00:03.900 --> 00:07.100
This could go away. There's confusion
as to where in the car the drugs were.

00:06.900 --> 00:10.200
- Understood.
- They may vow to the coke as found property and let you go.

00:10.200 --> 00:13.600
I got a bad feeling on that place,
and I don't think you should be involved.

00:13.600 --> 00:16.700
My whole life, Bobby, I never turned a buck.
I got a chance at that now.

00:16.600 --> 00:20.000
You want to be a wiseguy, then be
a wiseguy. Don't be half a wiseguy.

00:19.900 --> 00:21.900
- I tried to help you before.
- Nah, you didn't try.

00:21.900 --> 00:24.000
- I warned you.
- You didn't warn me, Bobby!

00:24.000 --> 00:26.800
I did everything except give the exact time
that bust was going down.

